   113вҶ’## Examples & Demos
   123вҶ’## API
   127вҶ’#### Table of Contents
   129вҶ’-   [mitt](#mitt)
   130вҶ’-   [all](#all)
   131вҶ’-   [on](#on)
   132вҶ’    -   [Parameters](#parameters)
   133вҶ’-   [off](#off)
